{"tid":1427362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果政府對活動以黎既所有被捕人士撤控, 但同時唔查呢段時期既狗隻濫權","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:09:02.000Z","uid":174941,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10fde3b077169c1cd6695540a3ff6d24952aef8e","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"雖則係天方夜譚,<br />\n但如果有咁既OFFER<br />\n大家會唔會妥協?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先救義士, 之後先睇下點搞濫權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />妥佢老母, 五大訴求 缺一不可, 寧攬炒 不赦狗<br />\n<br />\n但最壞打算可能係, 今次我 下次你, 永遠冇狗落鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6839238de754fc94f6e1122d42c22e2a7515ef92","tid":1427362,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"da2de27915c0ad3d8e8515473f1e08fdd08f2301","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"唔係散播失敗論<br />\n因為依家冇咁既OFFER<br />\n所以依家係要繼續爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9141c301b7cfc857657f86a53a52324aba215c7","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e648cc2ab43ed78efea7c2055ee1105968a62b5d","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"8月5號黃大仙被落單義士被控暴動罪<br />\n1430觀塘第一法庭提堂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1427350/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1427350/</a>"},{"pid":"a7eba87cbac739f3182bab0ad07a88f179c38d78","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"警方表示，八月五日全港多區的行動中，警方共拘捕148人，其中一名在黃大仙區拘捕的33歲姓李男子，已被暫控一項「參與暴動」罪及一項「未能出示身分證明文件」罪，案件將於今日（7日）下午在觀塘裁判法院提堂；另外，其中一名49歲姓何被捕男子，已被暫控一項「阻礙警務人員執行職務」罪，案件會於今日（7日）上午在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n一日就148位義士<br />\nD狗閪黑底就冇事<br />\n只係得一個半個被手足制服到<br />\n比佢地打呀斬呀果D手足仲多仲傷呀"},{"pid":"d34fcacd8b67640fcea81476b6af979ab3eb344b","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"56a735e0e146ea036d10757f9244f48461e453c1","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8b47cec4e33e2a43517d977de11bd41d421478ac","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d15ac6b5394b2bcb4e37c2a1ee83cbacbd84ed66","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f4021fae747f4dcd4995e7431da9f92a3aac90a7","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"7dfc849ffa15d27791db92ea2bb383c1428e70ef","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cc66d4d7fbf4cc6bae9f2f9a9bc1ab121a7a4bfc","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d261139fc2094565773c4ed391887011ddcbc5aa","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"20b1ca6087a14d03aea85204fe6d5875a7a3524b","tid":1427362,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"997db9a8307d7a7e0a0adf49aabeb14b8a295fbf","tid":1427362,"u